**Job Position:** Sales Consultant 

**Key Responsibilities:**

- Work within a high performing sales team
- Making sales in a residential construction environment
- Understanding of the new home market

**Key Skills & Competencies:**

- Sales experience, particularly in a similar role
- Proven track record of sales in a residential construction environment
- Strong understanding of the new home market
- Background in sales
- Excellent communication skills
- Well-presented and professional demeanor 

